for (reg in 1:8){
  write(paste("Exemple: ",reg),"")
  X<-dd8[dd8$REG==reg,"X"]
  Y<-dd8[dd8$REG==reg,"Y"]
  scatterplot(X,Y,smooth=F,box=F,main=reg)
  mod<-lm(Y~X)
  summary(mod)
}
